Steps for Implementing BroadCast Receiever.

1)Create a class that extends BroadCastReceiever.
2)OverRide Onreceieve method to provide implementation.
3)OnReceieve intent Local variable get the Action required.
4)Check the intent Action for the Receiever.


In the MainActivity/Activity.

1)Regsiter the Receiever in OnStart()
2)UnRegister in OnStop

In manifest file Declare the permission.